{"id": "1506256166290981028", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "365795813915492352", "author_name": "tgp495", "author_bot": false, "content": "毒編成作りたいんですが今回のローテピックアップで引いといた方がいいキャラっていますか？", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T11:24:14.930000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-19T11:24:26.969000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1506256801732235387", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "365795813915492352", "author_name": "tgp495", "author_bot": false, "content": "初心者でまだほとんどキャラがいなくて誰から引けばいいのかわからんので教えてもらえると助かります", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T11:26:46.431000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1506264838198923346", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 19, "author_id": "457896681367666690", "author_name": "shun5984", "author_bot": false, "content": "融災のレベル5（高難易度コンテンツ）を安定してクリアできる毒パーティです。\n限定キャラの優先度は下記の通りです。\n\n徐＞＞溶融ドール（OE）＞リリー", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T11:58:42.474000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-19T12:04:14.542000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["365795813915492352"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1506264838530138263", "filename": "Morimens_Screenshot_2026.05.19_-_20.54.42.91.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2902939, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1300659436804640788/1506264838530138263/Morimens_Screenshot_2026.05.19_-_20.54.42.91.png?ex=6a0da1f2&is=6a0c5072&hm=9a3c27ddab040885a876575c9f90dbf00780cedb4da658b6f04ba25a5a456bb9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1506256166290981028", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1506265553147527379", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "457896681367666690", "author_name": "shun5984", "author_bot": false, "content": "・徐は必須ですが、E0（凸なし）でokです。\n・ドールはOE（8体引く）がほぼ必須ですが、リソースの都合があれば月1で交換できる精神体カプセルでゆっくり凸っても良いと思います（ドールを使う場合は命輪もほぼ必須です）。\n・節約したい場合、リリーは恒常のファイントというキャラに置き換えても良いです。", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T12:01:32.931000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-19T12:03:32.815000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1506267654653087774", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 19, "author_id": "365795813915492352", "author_name": "tgp495", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます！全員持ってないので頑張って集めてみます！\nこのゲーム7凸が必須なキャラとかいるんですね、大変そうだ", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T12:09:53.969000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["457896681367666690"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1506265553147527379", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1506270679077490879", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "457896681367666690", "author_name": "shun5984", "author_bot": false, "content": "ドール以外は大体2凸くらいで十分なので、例外みたいなものですね。他に気に入るキャラとかが出てくるかもしれないので焦らず強化していけばよいと思います。\n繰り返しですが、ショップの精神体カプセルは万能凸アイテムなので忘れずに交換するのをオススメします！", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T12:21:55.048000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1506270679195062343", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1132556, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1300659436804640788/1506270679195062343/image.png?ex=6a0da763&is=6a0c55e3&hm=16d97fb55853c3c2030b0f1b21cb8ba3e9f704c05920c3c038f170e8ae6ef107&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1506271363382382652", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 19, "author_id": "365795813915492352", "author_name": "tgp495", "author_bot": false, "content": "何もわからないので情報を教えてもらえるのすごい助かります！\n精神体カプセルってやつですね買っておきます～", "timestamp": "2026-05-19T12:24:38.199000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["457896681367666690"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "24_smile", "emoji_id": "1459073862544130131", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1506270679077490879", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
